The number and address he left
are no longer valid.

00:42:03.939 --> 00:42:06.979
The remains were found in Tuba Township?

00:42:07.779 --> 00:42:09.339
It's about three kilometers away.

00:42:09.339 --> 00:42:10.899
But it's a different village.

00:42:11.259 --> 00:42:13.018
Any relatives or friends?

